; ── 3×3 Intersection Grid ────────────────────────────────
; Intersection mesh: 16×16m. Grid positions: -60, 0, +60
; Spacing 60m → gap between edges: 60-8-8 = 44m
; Road mesh 20×0.1×6, scale 2.2× = 44m to fill gap exactly
; EW road: Transform3D(2.2,0,0, 0,1,0, 0,0,1, X, 0.55, Z)
; NS road: Transform3D(0,0,-2.2, 0,1,0, 1,0,0, X, 0.55, Z)

